title: The Gary Null Show
content:
GUEST: EVELYN PRINGLE Guest Evelyn Pringle is an award-winning investigative journalist focused on exposing corruption... <!--more--> in government and in American corporations.
Over the past 8 years, she has written numerous exposes on the psycho-pharmaceutical complex with a focus on the government and drug-maker cartel that has a mission to over-medicate children.
In 2009 she aided Senator Grassleyâ€™s office in compiling data on TeenScreen and the pharmaceutical front organizations pushing for the drugging of US children.
